{"tid":1970624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥與司局長開會　期間觀看許冠傑網上演唱會","createTime":"2020-04-13T09:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T09:41:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ebc96a251877a9d79a21f86dd9edca49fe7c3bf3","tid":1970624,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"4月12日，香港特區行政長官林鄭月娥在社交專頁表示，下午與司局長及多名公務員開會，檢視疫情發展及商討第二輪&ldquo;防疫抗疫基金&rdquo;的具體安排，期間透過視像觀賞歌手許冠傑在網上演唱會，演唱歌曲《同舟共濟》。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0413/819825.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c5b6956cc98841cf74da5b0e377e47633384b8ae","tid":1970624,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"蛇王就蛇王啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"0f4fd5c498daf9bb4e79f4b60542b74f58dc6f20","tid":1970624,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}